==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: unable to recognize the true face of [[w:Mount Lushan|Mount Lushan]]
===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' bù shì lúshān zhēn miànmù)
#  to not recognize someone when you see them (despite the fact that you should know who the person is)

